## 📋 Project Overview
This project demonstrates **end-to-end Manual QA Testing** on the **[SauceDemo](https://saucedemo.com)** application, covering critical e-commerce user flows.

### 🔍 Scope
- Authentication (Login)
- Product Inventory
- Cart Operations
- Checkout Process

### 🧪 Testing Types
- Manual Testing  
- Functional Testing  
- Exploratory Testing  

### 💻 Environment
- Browser: Google Chrome (Desktop)

