## 🔍 QA Insights

### 🧠 Key Findings
- Weak validation in checkout flow (critical business flaw)  
- Delayed UI responses affecting usability  
- Inconsistent UX patterns across pages  

### 🚀 Recommendations
- [ ] Enforce validation rules for checkout  
- [ ] Improve UI responsiveness (real-time updates)  
- [ ] Standardize UI components and interactions  
- [ ] Improve error messaging clarity  

